1.5.name: wordpress/fha-mortgage-rates
1.5.description: This plugin installs a customizable FHA Mortgage Rates Widget that you can drag into your sidebar in the widget area of wordpress. The FHA mortgage rates widget is updated daily by FreeRateUpdate.com who researches wholesale mortgage lender's rate sheets and updates their FHA mortgage rates multiple times per day.
